<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="H" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Hunts-up" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Hunts-up,</orth> a tune played to wake sportsmen: <cit><quote>hunting thee hence with h. to the day,</quote> <bibl n="shak. rom 3.5.34" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. III, 5, 34</bibl></cit> (the full form <emph>the hunt is up</emph> in <bibl n="shak. tit 2.2.1" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. II, 2, 1</bibl>).
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>